title: 1930's Louis Vuitton Hardside Suitcase
description: 1930's Louis Vuitton hardside suitcase, 70 size, in classic stamped monogram pattern with tacked leather trim surround in embossed LV stripe. Case is with reinforced brass mounted corners, brass wrapped sides at top, LV stamped rivets and classic lock and latch closure with yellow stitched vachetta leather handle. Interior is canvas lined retaining tag reading 'Louis Vuitton LV 772025 Paris 70 Champs-Elysees 149 New Bond St. London W Nice Jardin Alberti Lille 34 Rue Faidherbe', without interior tray. Lock reads with patent, Louis Vuitton, 149 New Bond Street London 70 Champs Elysees London 059923 Made in France, latches with LV stamp at front.  Includes key and luggage tag, which needs strap repaired,

title: Fiddle Leaf Fig Plant in Pot
description: Fiddle Leaf Fig is 1 of the most popular house plants on the market. Tough, adaptable and unique, it adds a dramatic flair to any indoor space. Its large, waxy leaves stand out in any room or space. Low maintenance and easy to grow, Fiddle Leaf Fig makes an excellent houseplant for gardeners in any part of the country.

title: Oriental Furniture 36 in. Floral Blue and White Porcelain Tung Chi Vase
description:
Authentic oriental design decorative Tung Chi Vase. Akin to those used in palaces and temples in Ming dynasty era China. Classic formal 19th century style American and European decor, as well as a modern casual, eclectic home decor accent.
Beautiful Chinese porcelain
Traditional temple design with narrow neck and wide rim
Hand painted
Opening measures 5.75 in. dia.
High quality construction
Elegant design
